isfied.\n\n6. **Final Calculation:**\n   - After iterating, determine the smallest radius that satisfies all constraints.\n\nBased on these calculations, the reliable radius (R) for the heat shield is determined to be 1.5 meters.", config=ConfigFile(r=1.5)), 'passed': False, 'evaluation_result': {'r': 1.5, 'q_max_W_per_cm2': 4267678.087535678, 'Q_J_per_m2': 339866539.0314596, 'a_max_mps2': 80.39806839434318, 'passed': False}, 'score': 70}
